---
const credentials = [
  "Certified Life Coach & Yoga Teacher",
  "Reiki Master Practitioner",
  "Former Banking Executive & Economist",
  "Based in Brazil, serving clients worldwide",
];
---

<section id="about" class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-image-wrapper" data-reveal>
        <figure class="about-image">
          <img
            src="/images/coach-portrait.jpg"
            alt="Professional executive coach with warm, approachable demeanor in natural light"
            loading="lazy"
            width="400"
            height="500"
          />
        </figure>
        <div class="image-accent"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-content" data-reveal>
        <span class="section-subtitle">About Sylvie</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">
          From Corporate Success to Aligned Living
        </h2>

        <div class="about-story">
          <p>
            I understand what it's like to have everything society says you should want—and still
            feel empty. For years, I climbed the ladder in banking, achieving success after success,
            but something was missing.
          </p>
          <p>
            My transformation began when I stopped chasing what I thought I <em>should</em> want and
            started listening to what my heart was telling me. I left my corporate career, trained as a
            life coach, yoga teacher, and reiki practitioner, and moved to Brazil to create a life that
            truly aligned with my purpose.
          </p>
          <p>
            Now I help people just like you discover their unique mission on earth. I believe <strong>we
            all have a specific purpose, and when we find it and serve it, abundance flows naturally.</strong>
            Your dreams and what brings you joy aren't distractions—they're signposts pointing you toward
            your true calling.
          </p>
          <p>
            Together, we'll explore coaching, yoga, reiki, and conscious travel practices to help you
            reconnect with your authentic self and create the fulfilling life you're meant to live.
          </p>
        </div>

        <ul class="credentials-list">
          {credentials.map((credential) => (
            <li class="credential-item">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M3 8l3 3 7-7" stroke="var(--cta)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
              <span>{credential}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Breathing line divider -->
  <div class="section-divider">
    <div class="divider-breathing"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0 var(--space-2xl);
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-image {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    filter: grayscale(15%) contrast(1.02);
    transition: filter var(--duration-slow) var(--ease-calm);
  }

  .about-image:hover img {
    filter: grayscale(0%) contrast(1);
  }

  .image-accent {
    position: absolute;
    inset: var(--space-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.3;
    z-index: -1;
    transform: translate(var(--space-md), var(--space-md));
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 580px;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-widest);
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: var(--weight-normal);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .about-story {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .about-story p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about-story p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-story strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .credentials-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding-top: var(--space-md);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .credential-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .credential-item svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .section-divider {
    padding-top: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .about-image-wrapper {
      max-width: 400px;
    }
  }
</style>
